### Create Delivery
POST {{Eroad_DeliveryTracking_Command_API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/CreateDelivery
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "{{deliveryId}}",
  "routeId": "{{routeId}}"
}

### Update Delivery Status
PUT {{Eroad_DeliveryTracking_Command_API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/UpdateDeliveryStatus/{{deliveryId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "oldStatus": 0,
  "newStatus": 1
}

### Update Current Checkpoint
PUT {{Eroad_DeliveryTracking_Command_API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/UpdateCurrentCheckpoint/{{deliveryId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "checkpoint": "Main Distribution Center"
}

### Report Incident
POST {{Eroad_DeliveryTracking_Command_API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/ReportIncident/{{deliveryId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "incident": {
    "id": "{{incidentId}}",
    "type": "Vehicle Breakdown",
    "reportedTimestamp": "2026-01-24T10:30:00Z",
    "description": "Engine overheating",
    "resolved": false
  }
}

### Resolve Incident
PUT {{Eroad_DeliveryTracking_Command_API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/ResolveIncident/{{deliveryId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "incidentId": "{{incidentId}}"
}

### Capture Proof of Delivery
POST {{Eroad_DeliveryTracking_Command_API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/CaptureProofOfDelivery/{{deliveryId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
